               </msIdentifier>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>Images 5r-167r: Psalter. The midpoint of the Psalms is unmarked. Psalm 151 has the short version with some elements of the longer. The Song of Songs is the common version. Praises of Mary begins on Monday and culminates on Sunday. Illuminations are painted recently over text. The manuscript has been foliated in Arabic numbers in the lower right corner of each folio.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <textLang/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
